                "Commentary": "PLAYER OF THE MATCH - Hardik Pandya is the recipient of the award for his unbeaten and impactful 23-ball 50-run knock. Pandya says that he is pretty happy with his batting effort. Adds that he had to reassess the conditions. Tells that he tried to hit a bit too hard early on, but realised that he could just time the ball. Mentions that they were all keeping an eye on the South Africa versus West Indies game, but once they started, the focus completely shifted to this game and what they needed to execute. Says that he is satisfied with his bowling, and God has gifted him the ability to swing it both ways to make the batters work. Ends by saying that he still has one over to bowl (as he only bowled 3 in the game), which he will do now.",
