                "Commentary": "India brush aside Zimbabwe - A thumping win for the defending champions, and with this victory, they set up a virtual quarterfinal with the West Indies on Sunday. As a result of this outcome in Chennai, South Africa are now through to the semis, and Zimbabwe are out of the race. The Chevrons came into the Super 8s brimming with confidence after topping their group and beating the likes of Australia and Sri Lanka, but found themselves batted out of the game in both games, first by West Indies and tonight by India.",
